na del coco</h3><p>No sabemos ustedes, pero nosotros no teníamos idea qué era la <strong>\"manzana del coco\"</strong>. </p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-video-card kg-width-regular\" data-kg-thumbnail=\"https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/2022/05/media-thumbnail-ember380.jpg\" data-kg-custom-thumbnail=\"https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/2023/07/IMG_20230730_135017.jpg\">\n            <div class=\"kg-video-container\">\n                <video src=\"https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/media/2022/05/manzanadelcoco.mp4\" poster=\"https://img.spacergif.org/v1/720x960/0a/spacer.png\" width=\"720\" height=\"960\" playsinline=\"\" preload=\"metadata\" style=\"background: transparent url('https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/2023/07/IMG_20230730_135017.jpg') 50% 50% / cover no-repeat;\"></video>\n                <div class=\"kg-video-overlay\">\n                    <button class=\"kg-video-large-play-icon\" aria-label=\"Play video\">\n                        <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\">\n                            <path d=\"M23.14 10.608 2.253.164A1.559 1.559 0 0 0 0 1.557v20.887a1.558 1.558 0 0 0 2.253 1.392L23.14 13.393a1.557 1.557 0 0 0 0-2.785Z\"></path>\n                        </svg>\n                    </button>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"kg-video-player-container\">\n                    <div class=\"kg-video-player\">\n                        <button class=\"kg-video-play-icon\" aria-label=\"Play video\">\n                            <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\">\n                                <path d=\"M23.14 10.608 2.253.164A1.559 1.559 0 0 0 0 1.557v20.887a1.558 1.558 0 0 0 2.253 1.392L23.14 13.393a1.557 1.557 0 0 0 0-2.785Z\"></path>\n                            </svg>\n        