51 0 0 1 8.515 17a.245.245 0 0 1 .177.075 10.081 10.081 0 0 0 6.5 2.92 1 1 0 0 0 1.061-1V9.266a.247.247 0 0 1 .073-.176Z\"></path>\n                            </svg>\n                        </button>\n                        <input type=\"range\" class=\"kg-video-volume-slider\" max=\"100\" value=\"100\">\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            \n        </figure><p>La manzana del coco crece dentro del mismo cuando el coco comienza a germinar, o sea, cuando comienza a desarrollarse la semilla para que crezca una nueva palma. </p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card kg-card-hascaption\"><img src=\"https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/2022/05/Copy-of-DSC_9514_Momentedit.jpg\" class=\"kg-image\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1080\" srcset=\"https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/size/w600/2022/05/Copy-of-DSC_9514_Momentedit.jpg 600w, https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/size/w1000/2022/05/Copy-of-DSC_9514_Momentedit.jpg 1000w, https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/size/w1600/2022/05/Copy-of-DSC_9514_Momentedit.jpg 1600w, https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/2022/05/Copy-of-DSC_9514_Momentedit.jpg 1920w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"><figcaption><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">manzana del coco</span></figcaption></figure><p>¡Y sabe espectacular!</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/2022/05/Screen-Shot-2022-05-17-at-13.40.58.png\" class=\"kg-image\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1122\" height=\"1492\" srcset=\"https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/size/w600/2022/05/Screen-Shot-2022-05-17-at-13.40.58.png 600w,